description: Freedom a la Cart is a free enterprise food cart and catering service that is fighting human trafficking by employing Columbus survivors of trafficking, empowering them toward sustainable livelihoods, and significantly aiding in the restoration of their lives.  Our employees learn vital life skills while producing first-class, yet affordable food.  Freedom a la Cart funds some of the restorative programs of doma International, a local non-profit organization.The delectable food that Freedom produces is anything but a "compassion buy."  Using locally grown, organic ingredients whenever possible, our meals are creative fusions of delicious flavors and comforting tastes.
name: Freedom a la Cart
